## Project Page UI Enhancement

### Purpose

Enhanced the Projects page user interface to improve project visibility, navigation, and overall usability.

### Changes Implemented

* Replaced the traditional project display with an improved card-based layout.
* Added support for both compact column view and grid card view.
* Displayed project task counts directly on project cards.
* Improved project information presentation and readability.
* Enhanced spacing, alignment, and visual consistency across the Projects page.
* Optimized project navigation for managing multiple projects efficiently.
* Updated project card styling to align with the overall Project Management dashboard design.

### Outcome

The Projects page now provides a cleaner, more organized, and user-friendly experience, enabling users to quickly identify projects, view task statistics, and switch between different project layouts based on their preference.
